        "content": "YOUNG EVELYN:\nThe transfer is failing.\n\nHALE:\nNo. It's adapting.\n\nSYSTEM:\nUNAUTHORIZED NETWORK EXPANSION DETECTED.\n\nYOUNG NOAH:\nWhat does that mean?\n\nHALE:\nIt means Subject 01 is learning."
